'''二碳化钍'''是一种无机化合物，化学式为ThC<sub>2</sub>。它可由金属[[钍|钍]]和[[石墨|石墨]]在2000~2500 °C反应制得。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=73|issue=10|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=1951-10|pages=4777–4781|doi=10.1021/ja01154a090|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja01154a090|title=The Structure of Thorium Dicarbide by X-Ray and Neutron Diffraction 1|accessdate=2020-11-03|author=Elton B. Hunt, R. E. Rundle}}</ref>它可以在空气中迅速水解，生成[[二氧化钍|二氧化钍]]、[[氢气|氢气]]和碳氢化合物，其反应速率是相应二碳化铀的10倍。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Ceramic Society|volume=45|issue=3|language=en|issn=0002-7820|date=1962-03|pages=136–141|doi=10.1111/j.1151-2916.1962.tb11102.x|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1111/j.1151-2916.1962.tb11102.x|title=Reaction-Rate Studies of Thorium-Uranium Dicarbides in Moist Air|accessdate=2020-11-03|author=G. B. Engle, W. V. Goeddel, C. S. Luby}}</ref>它也能和酸反应，如和[[硫酸|硫酸]]反应，生成[[硫酸钍|硫酸钍]]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Nature|volume=195|issue=4838|language=en|issn=0028-0836|date=1962-07|pages=267–268|doi=10.1038/195267a0|url=http://www.nature.com/articles/195267a0|title=Acid Leaching of Thorium Carbide|accessdate=2020-11-03|author=Yasuichi Sasaki, Fujio Ichikawa, Hisashi Imai, Shinobu Uruno}}</ref>

